		"name": "AI Codebase Copilot API",
		"description": "API collection for verifying the AI Codebase Copilot FastAPI backend directly (default: http://localhost:8000/v1). Run Register (once), Login (captures token), Create Project (captures projectId), then Add Repository, Trigger Indexing (captures snapshotId), and Chat.",
